INSTALLATION & RUNNING
=======================

1. Extract the bill_splitter folder
2. Open terminal in the bill_splitter directory
3. Run: ./run.sh

The application will:
- Create a virtual environment
- Install dependencies
- Start on http://localhost:5000

Default port: 5000
Database: SQLite (bill_splitter.db)

MANUAL INSTALLATION
===================

python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
